It's reported that

00:32:12.960 --> 00:32:13.940
recently the Japanese army

00:32:13.960 --> 00:32:16.700
has launched fierce offensives
in Northern Jiangsu and Northern Anhui.

00:32:22.200 --> 00:32:24.900
Three prongs of their forces
are about to encircle Baimahu.

00:32:25.920 --> 00:32:29.220
Villagers there are mobilizing
for armed resistance.

00:32:29.720 --> 00:32:30.700
Baimahu.

00:32:32.150 --> 00:32:33.180
My mother's still back home,

00:32:33.200 --> 00:32:35.020
waiting for me to return
to Baimahu and care for her!

00:32:41.520 --> 00:32:42.530
Baimahu.

00:32:51.200 --> 00:32:52.330
Baimahu.

