[Battle of Nanchang]

00:33:15.200 --> 00:33:16.700
Battle of Nanchang.

00:33:32.560 --> 00:33:35.480
[Baimahu in Peril]

00:33:43.790 --> 00:33:45.570
We're just commoners.

00:33:45.590 --> 00:33:47.180
What's war got to do with us?

00:33:47.200 --> 00:33:49.290
By teaching the Japanese as Joseph Lee,

00:33:49.310 --> 00:33:51.610
you've opened the gates for them.

00:33:56.200 --> 00:33:57.570
Baimahu in peril...

00:34:10.630 --> 00:34:11.210
Gu Yangshan, open the gate!

00:34:12.150 --> 00:34:13.170
Baimahu is in peril!

00:34:13.270 --> 00:34:14.690
We can't let the Japanese through!

00:34:15.040 --> 00:34:16.090
Gu Yangshan, open the gate!

00:34:16.110 --> 00:34:16.690
Gu Yangshan!

00:34:17.670 --> 00:34:19.300
Gu Yangshan, I beg you!

00:34:19.320 --> 00:34:21.610
Open the gate,
I need to go back to Baimahu!

00:34:22.920 --> 00:34:25.170
I'm begging you, Gu Yangshan!

00:34:26.190 --> 00:34:27.170
Open it!

00:34:27.710 --> 00:34:28.690
What's wrong?

00:34:29.190 --> 00:34:30.170
Gu Yangshan!

00:34:30.440 --> 00:34:31.170
Tell me,

00:34:31.400 --> 00:34:32.570
what's the situation at Baimahu now?

00:34:32.590 --> 00:34:33.780
How is it now?

00:34:40.110 --> 00:34:41.170
Given the current circumstances,

00:34:42.880 --> 00:34:45.170
Baimahu won't last 72 hours.

00:34:51.110 --> 00:34:51.780
Then what should we do?

00:34:53.590 --> 00:34:54.170
Right.

00:34:54.710 --> 00:34:57.530
Isn't your father some commander?

00:34:57.550 --> 00:34:59.780
Get him to dispatch troops
to protect Baimahu,

00:34:59.800 --> 00:35:01.170
and my mother!

00:35:06.710 --> 00:35:07.250
Forget it.

00:35:08.040 --> 00:35:09.250
I knew I couldn't count on you.

00:35:10.110 --> 00:35:11.570
I'll go back myself to save my mother.

00:35:11.710 --> 00:35:13.170
Don't stop me!

00:35:13.190 --> 00:35:14.170
I want to save Baimahu

00:35:14.190 --> 00:35:15.570
and your mother too,

00:35:15.590 --> 00:35:16.780
but what can I do?

00:35:16.800 --> 00:35:18.570
The Japanese army
is at Baimahu right now.

00:35:18.590 --> 00:35:19.170
We have no idea

00:35:19.190 --> 00:35:20.570
about their operational plans.

00:35:20.590 --> 00:35:23.090
Even if reinforcements go,
it's just sending them to die.

00:35:23.110 --> 00:35:24.690
If you go back alone, what can you do?

00:35:24.710 --> 00:35:26.690
You can't even get inside on your own!

00:35:30.190 --> 00:35:30.690
Then what?

00:35:33.630 --> 00:35:35.460
I can't just leave my mother to die!

00:35:37.880 --> 00:35:39.570
That's why the priority now

00:35:39.880 --> 00:35:42.300
is to replace the enemy's
operational code.

